OL,3,CMan died after 999 call was
OL,4,Cincorrectly downgraded
OL,6,FA man who collapsed and later died
OL,7,Fcould have potentially survived had it
OL,8,Fnot been for failings by the Welsh
OL,9,FAmbulance Service Trust, a new Public
OL,10,FService Ombudsman for Wales report has
OL,11,Ffound.
OL,13,FMartyn Wright, 35, died after
OL,14,Fcollapsing at his home in December
OL,15,F2022.
OL,17,FA post-mortem examination later found
OL,18,Fthat he died from Ketoacidosis - a
OL,19,Fcondition where toxins build up in the
OL,20,Fblood.
