OL,3,CMan died after 999 call was
OL,4,Cincorrectly downgraded
OL,6,FAn investigation by the Ombudsman into
OL,7,FMartyn's death found that as well as
OL,8,Fincorrectly downgrading the call from
OL,9,Fred - reserved for the most serious
OL,10,Femergencies - to a green, the trust
OL,11,Falso gave the family incorrect
OL,12,Finformation about administering CPR
OL,13,Fand the attending paramedic entered
OL,14,Fincorrect information on the clinical
OL,15,Frecord.
OL,17,FFollowing the incident, the report
OL,18,Fraised concerns about the robustness
OL,19,Fof the complaints process within the
OL,20,Fambulance trust and that significant
OL,21,Fevidence was not handed over.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/18
