OL,3,CMan died after 999 call was
OL,4,Cincorrectly downgraded
OL,6,FMartyn's mother Claire Wright says she
OL,7,Fhas spent 22 months looking for
OL,8,Fanswers regarding the failings that
OL,9,Fled to her son's death - primarily why
OL,10,Fthe initial call was downgraded.
OL,12,FDespite taking around 25 minutes to
OL,13,Fget to Martyn's home, she still
OL,14,Farrived before the ambulance.
OL,16,F"When I got there it was a sight I'll
OL,17,Fnever forget. I went into the house
OL,18,FMartyn was unconscious, John was busy
OL,19,Fdoing chest compressions and doing the
OL,20,Fbest for his brother.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/18
