PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F468A1742533813
OL,3,CMan died after 999 call was
OL,4,Cincorrectly downgraded
OL,6,F"There was no sign of an ambulance
OL,7,Fwhich I couldn't quite understand as I
OL,8,Fthought by the time I got there I felt
OL,9,Fthere would be somebody there.
OL,11,F"So I rang again, and as a result of
OL,12,Fthat phone call an ambulance was
OL,13,Fdeployed and turned up some 10 minutes
OL,14,For so later."
OL,16,FShe said that the whole family have
OL,17,Fhad many questions about Martyn's
OL,18,Fdeath and treatment.
OL,20,F"The last couple of years has been
OL,21,Fhorrific on so many levels.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/18
