PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F468A1742533813
OL,3,CMan died after 999 call was
OL,4,Cincorrectly downgraded
OL,6,F"Certainly very early on questions
OL,7,Fneeded to be asked because we were
OL,8,Faware the ambulance hadn't come
OL,9,Fquickly which is what my son certainly
OL,10,Fexpected when he rang.
OL,12,F"We later found out that the initial
OL,13,Fresponse vehicle was stood down after
OL,14,Fa number of minutes by the call
OL,15,Fhandler."
OL,17,FMrs Wright says the call handler
OL,18,Fassigned the call was inexperienced
OL,19,Fand had made incorrect assumptions
OL,20,Fabout when Martyn had collapsed.
