OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F468A1742533813
OL,3,CMan died after 999 call was
OL,4,Cincorrectly downgraded
OL,6,F"We put in a concern (with the Trust)
OL,7,Fpretty much immediately because we
OL,8,Fwere so perplexed. We wanted to know
OL,9,Fwhat happened.
OL,11,F"Why was there such a delay? Why
OL,12,Fwasn't Martyn given whatever he needed
OL,13,Fto at least give him a chance?
OL,15,F"He was fit, he was young, surely he
OL,16,Fmay well have had a chance - at least
OL,17,Fa fair chance - of survival had they
OL,18,Fgot there in time. It's hard for us to
OL,19,Fthink what if.
