OL,3,CMan died after 999 call was
OL,4,Cincorrectly downgraded
OL,6,F"As far as John was concerned he had
OL,7,Frung for an ambulance and he fully
OL,8,Fthought it was coming.
OL,10,F"For John to try and save his brother
OL,11,Ffor an extended period of time like
OL,12,Fthat, how do you deal with that?"
OL,14,FMrs Wright said the family's concerns
OL,15,Fhave been compounded by the ambulance
OL,16,Fservice's response to the Ombudsman's
OL,17,Finvestigation.
