OL,6,F"Its quite shocking how they deflect,
OL,7,Fembellish what they want to and play
OL,8,Fdown what they don't want to depending
OL,9,Fon how it makes them look."
OL,11,FIn its report the Ombudsman also
OL,12,Freviewed a second case in which a 93-
OL,13,Fyear-old woman died after waiting 16
OL,14,Fhours for an ambulance after falling
OL,15,Fat home.
