OL,4,Cincorrectly downgraded
OL,6,FThe Ombudsman found that in that
OL,7,Finstance the trust had correctly
OL,8,Ftriaged and prioritised the calls but
OL,9,Fthat her case should have been
OL,10,Freviewed by a clinician and considered
OL,11,Fescalating the response category.
OL,13,FNow Martyn's family say the service
OL,14,Fprovided by the Welsh Ambulance
OL,15,FService has become a "lottery".
OL,17,F"I want people to realise that even in
OL,18,Fa 999 life threatening situation you
OL,19,Fcannot rely on the emergence service.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/18
