OL,3,CMan died after 999 call was
OL,4,Cincorrectly downgraded
OL,6,F"I don't wish to scaremonger but I
OL,7,Fthink it is important people realise
OL,8,Fbecause I wouldn't want anyone else to
OL,9,Fexperience what we have experienced.
OL,11,F"What we have learned I think is that
OL,12,Fit is a lottery now, I wouldn't wish
OL,13,Fit on my worst enemy.
OL,15,F"Just recently my very elderly
OL,16,Fneighbour had a fall at home and
OL,17,Fobviously needed an ambulance, three
OL,18,Fambulances were parked outside her
OL,19,Fhouse.
