OL,6,FIn response to the Ombudsman report,
OL,7,FLiam Williams, Executive Director of
OL,8,FQuality and Nursing at the Welsh
OL,9,FAmbulance Service, said: "On behalf of
OL,10,Feveryone at the Welsh Ambulance
OL,11,FService, I would like to extend my
OL,12,Fdeepest sympathies to the loved ones
OL,13,Fof both Mr B and Mrs C respectively on
OL,14,Ftheir sad loss.
OL,16,F"We always seek to provide the best
OL,17,Fpossible care at all times and deeply
OL,18,Fregret those occasions when that has
OL,19,Fnot been achieved.
