OL,6,F"We have been working closely with the
OL,7,FPublic Services Ombudsman Wales over
OL,8,Fmany months, reviewing each case in
OL,9,Fdetail to maximise the learnings for
OL,10,Ffuture.
OL,12,F"Our commitment to improving the
OL,13,Fexperience and outcomes for patients
OL,14,Fand their loved ones when they contact
OL,15,Fus is absolute, and we have already
OL,16,Fimplemented a number of the measures
OL,17,Fthat were agreed.
