OL,6,F"We are grateful to the Ombudsman for
OL,7,Fher recommendations, which we fully
OL,8,Faccept, and would once again like to
OL,9,Foffer our condolences to both families
OL,10,Fon their loss."
OL,12,FCommenting on the report, Public
OL,13,FServices Ombudsman for Wales, Michelle
OL,14,FMorris, said:"I would like to extend
OL,15,Fmy sincerest condolences to both
OL,16,Ffamilies for their sad losses."
