OL,3,CMan died after 999 call was
OL,4,Cincorrectly downgraded
OL,6,F"The failures revealed in these
OL,7,Freports raise serious concerns about
OL,8,Fhow emergency calls were handled and
OL,9,Ftriaged by the Trust. The failings led
OL,10,Fto serious injustice for both families
OL,11,Fand had correct actions been taken
OL,12,Fthen the treatment and outcomes for
OL,13,Fboth patients could have been
OL,14,Fdifferent. I am also concerned about
OL,15,Fthe robustness of the Trust's
OL,16,Finvestigations of the complaints it
OL,17,Freceives."
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@JO]
