OL,3,CMan died after 999 call was
OL,4,Cincorrectly downgraded
OL,6,F"The Putting Things Right Regulations,
OL,7,Funder which the Trust responded to the
OL,8,Fcomplaints, places an obligation upon
OL,9,Fit to investigate concerns properly,
OL,10,Fefficiently and openly. Furthermore
OL,11,Fthe Duty of Candour is now a statutory
OL,12,Frequirement placed on health boards."
OL,14,F"The responses provided by the Trust
OL,15,Fto both complainants fell well short
OL,16,Fof what the Putting Things Right
OL,17,FRegulations and the NHS Wales Duty of
OL,18,FCandour promote and are intended to
OL,19,Fachieve."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@eO]vD@AOU{D@IO]
