OL,3,CMan died after 999 call was
OL,4,Cincorrectly downgraded
OL,6,F"I have made a number of
OL,7,Frecommendations, accepted by the
OL,8,FTrust, to address the failures
OL,9,Fidentified in both investigations. In
OL,10,Fthe future, the Trust also needs to
OL,11,Fensure that it responds openly and
OL,12,Fhonestly to complaints, and that staff
OL,13,Finvolved in the response also need to
OL,14,Freflect on both the duty, and their
OL,15,Fown professional standards obligations
OL,16,Fwhen doing so."
